items.name: Pickled Goods & Olives Oloves Lemony Lover Olives
items.details: Pitted green olives with lemon & garlic. The healthy olive snack. 50 calorie snack. Lemony Lover -a zesty blend of lemon pieces, oregano and a hint of garlic. The taste of sunshine! In Barcelona we had a dream, to make a cool snack that we would love to eat. That's why we created Oloves, delicious, natural, deli-style olives. Oloves are the healthy alternative snack with no preservatives and only 50 calories per bag. The ready to eat treat with no pits, no liquid, just pure healthy goodness and of course: a little love in every olive! No major allergens. Vegetarian & vegan. Naturally low in saturated fat. 12+ olives per bag. May contain stones/pits. Packed in a protective atmosphere. Made in Morocco.
items.directions: Once opened refrigerate and consume within 48 hours.
items.ingredients: Pitted Green Olives 91%, Sunflower Oil, Lemon Pieces 3%, Garlic, Oregano, Salt, Vinegar, Acidifiers: Lactic Acid and Citric Acid.
